ReturnPolicy.Description:
In the unlikely event of an item needing to be returned to Planet Vintage, the customer must contact Pegathith through ebay message and all items must be of the same quality as originally sent and within 14 days of receipt of the goods.
The customer is liable for all return postage and packaging fees.
